Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?Phase=202:=20Punch=20layer=20=E2=80=94=20second?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20oscillator=20for=20percussive=20klap?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Adds a short tonal burst summed into the oscillator before the crossover
so it rides through the distortion chain together with the body's upper
band, giving the kick an extra percussive "klap" transient distinct from
the noise-based click layer (which mixes in parallel after distortion).

Params:
- punch_level (0..1, default 0)
- punch_freq (60..600 Hz, default 220)
- punch_decay (2..80 ms, default 12)
- punch_curve (0.1..8, default 2.0)

A dedicated SineOsc and Envelope are reset/triggered alongside the main
ones in fire() and reset(). The render path mirrors the same signal flow
for WAV export. All six presets gained punch defaults tuned to character.
UI grew a PUNCH panel in a new third row; window height bumped to 480.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
